Deal collect - leverages the content on different e commerce websites along with the power of the Social media such as aggregating mood about certain products from the social media space to build a recommender system to suggest better products to users along with other capabilities such as which particular e commerce portal in itself is more trusted among different users. This should allow the user to make a better choice among the products that he is buying to optimize on the different products and also ease the process of getting best value for money - POWER TO THE USER. !!
